org.baswell.routes

Class RoutesServlet

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.servlet.GenericServlet
      • javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet
        • org.baswell.routes.RoutesServlet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, javax.servlet.Servlet, javax.servlet.ServletConfig

    public class RoutesServlet
extends javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet

    An entry point for mapping HTTP servlet requests to route methods. All HTTP requests received by this servlet will be passed to RoutesEngine. If a routes match was found the request will be processed by that route otherwise this servlet will return a 404 (HttpServletResponse.setStatus(404)).

    See Also:
    RoutesFilter, RoutesEngine, Serialized Form
